WEBVTT

00:01:25.800 --> 00:01:30.800
"Sammy's Children's Day"

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:34.000
(Episode 2)

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:35.200
Boss! Boss!

00:01:35.359 --> 00:01:36.239
Boss, are you okay?

00:01:36.359 --> 00:01:37.359
Are you alright?

00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:38.480
Are you hurt, Boss?

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:40.760
Boss, your hand is bleeding so much!

00:01:41.239 --> 00:01:42.359
I'm fine.

00:01:44.519 --> 00:01:45.879
Why are you all shouting?

00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:48.840
How's your hand?

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:50.760
Boss, you've lost a lot of blood.

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:53.400
Ahao...

00:01:53.959 --> 00:01:54.959
Who's Ahao?

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:56.560
Ahao, are you okay?

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:58.239
I think that was Liuyi's old name.

00:01:58.280 --> 00:01:58.599
Sister...

00:01:58.760 --> 00:01:59.120
Sister!

00:01:59.480 --> 00:01:59.959
Ahao!

00:02:00.079 --> 00:02:01.079
I'm okay.

00:02:02.359 --> 00:02:03.359
What are you doing?

00:02:03.519 --> 00:02:04.519
What do you think you're doing?!

00:02:04.760 --> 00:02:05.760
Get lost!

00:02:06.400 --> 00:02:07.400
Get away from him!

00:02:09.919 --> 00:02:10.919
Back off!

00:02:12.039 --> 00:02:13.039
Sister...

00:02:17.319 --> 00:02:18.319
Get out of here!

00:02:18.479 --> 00:02:20.520
Don't you dare bully him!

00:02:21.879 --> 00:02:22.879
Get lost!

00:02:24.199 --> 00:02:25.360
Ma'am! Ma'am!

00:02:26.159 --> 00:02:27.159
Go!

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:28.599
Beat it!

00:02:28.919 --> 00:02:30.199
Back up! Everyone back up!

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:33.960
He's just a kid! Get lost!

00:02:34.719 --> 00:02:35.840
Nobody touches Ahao!

00:02:38.599 --> 00:02:39.599
Ahao...

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:44.280
Ahao!

00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:46.319
Ahao, are you hurt?

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:49.039
Did they hurt you, Ahao?

00:02:49.719 --> 00:02:50.960
Ahao, are you okay?

00:02:52.520 --> 00:02:53.599
It's all my fault.

00:02:53.639 --> 00:02:54.840
It's because of me.

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:55.240
Sister...

00:02:55.240 --> 00:02:56.000
It's all because of me.

00:02:56.039 --> 00:02:56.400
Sister!

00:02:56.479 --> 00:02:57.479
I'm the one to blame.

00:02:57.599 --> 00:02:58.800
I didn't protect you.

00:02:59.080 --> 00:03:00.080
Sister,

00:03:01.719 --> 00:03:02.719
it's me, Ahao.

00:03:06.599 --> 00:03:07.599
Look at me.

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:10.240
I'm fine now.

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:24.319
Ahao is perfectly fine.

00:03:26.599 --> 00:03:27.800
Ahao is okay.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:31.400
Ahao is okay.

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:33.639
He's alive and well.

00:03:40.759 --> 00:03:41.680
Ahao is fine.

00:03:41.719 --> 00:03:44.000
Sister, I'm taking you home.

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:47.879
Let's go home.

00:03:49.039 --> 00:03:50.120
Ahao is okay.

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:55.680
Let's go.

00:03:55.919 --> 00:03:56.240
Ahao...

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:57.080
Come on.

00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:58.400
Ahao!

00:04:01.080 --> 00:04:02.080
Stop looking.

00:04:08.639 --> 00:04:09.639
My backpack...

00:04:48.279 --> 00:04:49.319
Isn't that 'Twin-Blade Xia'?

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:50.600
Who's that guy with him?

00:04:51.480 --> 00:04:52.680
Doesn't look like a gangster.

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:55.360
What are you doing?

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:57.040
What do you think you're doing?

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:59.000
If my sister loses a single hair,

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:00.040
you're a dead man.

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:03.199
Can we take the back alleys?

00:05:04.399 --> 00:05:05.399
What are you afraid of?

00:05:05.879 --> 00:05:06.920
I'm right here.

00:05:08.959 --> 00:05:10.120
I'm just worried my dad will see me.

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:11.839
If he sees me with a gangster,

00:05:12.519 --> 00:05:13.519
he'll be worried sick.

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:17.480
I'm Twin-Blade Xia!

00:05:17.879 --> 00:05:18.879
What's there to fear?

00:05:19.160 --> 00:05:21.040
I shouldn't have to hide, okay?

00:05:21.959 --> 00:05:23.879
I should at least have that much clout.

00:05:25.240 --> 00:05:26.639
That's not what I meant.

00:05:29.959 --> 00:05:30.959
Fine, alleys it is.

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:34.680
Move it!

00:05:46.720 --> 00:05:47.720
How's your sister doing?

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:50.120
She's asleep.

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:52.480
Feel free to look around.

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:53.720
Okay.

00:06:12.519 --> 00:06:13.759
Cross the threshold of the hall,

00:06:14.480 --> 00:06:15.720
The soul of the rider stands tall.

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:17.920
Keep loyalty deep in your heart,

00:06:18.759 --> 00:06:19.920
Or two blades will tear you apart.

00:06:31.959 --> 00:06:32.959
Why aren't you coming in?

00:06:34.920 --> 00:06:37.040
I'm not joining the triads.

00:06:43.199 --> 00:06:44.240
You've learned a lot today.

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:45.759
You know too many of our secrets.

00:06:47.199 --> 00:06:48.199
If you don't cross that line,

00:06:51.160 --> 00:06:52.480
then I'll have no choice

00:06:53.199 --> 00:06:54.199
but to kill you.

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:08.000
You're not going to kill me.

00:07:08.519 --> 00:07:09.600
You just saved my life.

00:07:09.639 --> 00:07:11.040
Killing me now would be a waste of effort.

00:07:12.519 --> 00:07:13.800
Besides, I don't think you're the type

00:07:13.839 --> 00:07:15.120
to just kill people for no reason.

00:07:16.399 --> 00:07:17.279
You're the legendary Twin-Blade Xia

00:07:17.279 --> 00:07:18.879
of the Xiaoqi Hall.

00:07:19.480 --> 00:07:20.759
You're meant for greatness in the gang.

00:07:21.560 --> 00:07:23.879
I'm just an unarmed college student.

00:07:25.519 --> 00:07:26.720
I'm not even worth your time to kill.

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:36.480
I've gotta say,

00:07:43.319 --> 00:07:45.120
you're quite the smooth talker.

00:07:48.480 --> 00:07:49.879
A four-eyes like you

00:07:50.279 --> 00:07:51.480
wants to be my lackey?

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:52.680
I wouldn't even take you.

00:07:54.839 --> 00:07:56.199
Who said I wanted to be your lackey?

00:07:57.279 --> 00:07:58.319
Nobody's asking.

00:07:59.639 --> 00:08:00.639
Help me bandage this up.

00:08:03.079 --> 00:08:04.079
Okay.

00:08:08.839 --> 00:08:10.160
This might sting a bit.

00:08:10.680 --> 00:08:12.000
Just bear with it.

00:08:13.680 --> 00:08:14.680
Who do you think I am?

00:08:17.399 --> 00:08:18.240
I've been getting hurt

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:19.480
since before you could read.

00:08:19.480 --> 00:08:21.000
This is nothing.

00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:25.759
He Chusan, why are you being so rough?

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:29.240
I'm not!

00:08:29.480 --> 00:08:30.480
Stop faking it.

00:08:32.120 --> 00:08:33.679
I knew you were trouble.

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:35.799
Messing with the
script to play in my face,

00:08:36.279 --> 00:08:37.279
tattling to my sister...

00:08:37.799 --> 00:08:39.080
I can tell you're up to no good.

00:08:39.600 --> 00:08:40.600
Don't think I don't see through you.

00:08:40.879 --> 00:08:42.080
I just can't be bothered to deal with you.

00:08:45.000 --> 00:08:46.240
Well, aren't you the bigger man.

00:08:48.919 --> 00:08:49.919
Smart-ass.

00:08:52.919 --> 00:08:53.600
Xia Liuyi.

00:08:53.639 --> 00:08:54.639
Add "Brother" to that.

00:08:56.960 --> 00:08:57.960
Brother Liuyi.

00:08:59.639 --> 00:09:00.799
You have a cut on your face too.

00:09:01.480 --> 00:09:02.759
Come here, let me clean it.

00:09:25.159 --> 00:09:25.480
By the way,

00:09:25.960 --> 00:09:26.960
backstage back then,

00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:28.240
what did Xiaoman ask you?

00:09:32.360 --> 00:09:33.679
She asked me what love is.

00:09:37.039 --> 00:09:38.039
And what did you say?

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:40.240
I didn't get a chance to answer.

00:09:43.799 --> 00:09:44.960
Truth is, I don't really know either.

00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:48.039
This is the first love story I've ever written.

00:09:50.120 --> 00:09:51.480
It was terrible.

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:59.120
But I read somewhere

00:10:02.720 --> 00:10:03.720
that love

00:10:05.559 --> 00:10:06.919
is what happens

00:10:07.840 --> 00:10:08.720
when someone risks everything

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:10.759
to save another person.

00:10:24.840 --> 00:10:25.840
Brother Liuyi,

00:10:27.720 --> 00:10:29.120
why did you save me?

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:30.120
He Chusan,

00:10:36.039 --> 00:10:37.039
you really are

00:10:49.279 --> 00:10:50.679
incredibly annoying.

00:11:00.882 --> 00:11:06.135
[Three different books about
romanance or romance stories]

00:11:20.360 --> 00:11:21.360
Ah San!

00:11:24.960 --> 00:11:25.480
Ah San!

00:11:25.879 --> 00:11:26.879
You're back.

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:28.080
Look at you.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:29.840
You were out all night.

00:11:30.200 --> 00:11:31.320
You didn't even show up at Fei Jie's.

00:11:33.759 --> 00:11:34.759
What happened to your head?

00:11:35.480 --> 00:11:36.480
Tell me the truth.

00:11:36.519 --> 00:11:37.720
Did someone bully you out there?

00:11:38.360 --> 00:11:39.360
No.

00:11:39.559 --> 00:11:40.039
Dad,

00:11:40.080 --> 00:11:41.240
can you tell Fei Jie for me

00:11:41.480 --> 00:11:42.919
that I won't be in for the next two weeks?

00:11:44.279 --> 00:11:45.279
I've recently

00:11:45.759 --> 00:11:47.919
joined a new research project,

00:11:48.559 --> 00:11:49.559
and it's really busy.

00:11:52.080 --> 00:11:52.759
So yesterday,

00:11:53.080 --> 00:11:54.080
you were at school?

00:11:54.240 --> 00:11:55.240
Then your head...

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:58.120
A little black dog bit me.

00:11:59.639 --> 00:12:00.639
It's fine.

00:12:02.840 --> 00:12:03.840
By the way, Dad,

00:12:05.519 --> 00:12:06.519
I wanted to ask...

00:12:06.759 --> 00:12:07.759
If someone

00:12:08.200 --> 00:12:09.200
gets startled easily

00:12:09.559 --> 00:12:10.559
and then loses their grip on reality,

00:12:11.480 --> 00:12:12.679
is there a good prescription

00:12:13.360 --> 00:12:14.360
to help calm them down?

00:12:26.360 --> 00:12:27.600
Hey, college boy. You're early today.

00:12:33.879 --> 00:12:34.879
Brother Ma.

00:12:35.240 --> 00:12:36.559
No filming today?

00:12:36.759 --> 00:12:37.919
The Boss's wife is sick, so we're off.

00:12:38.559 --> 00:12:39.559
That little black dog...

00:12:41.679 --> 00:12:42.679
Where's Brother Liuyi?

00:12:48.600 --> 00:12:49.600
Who do you think you are?

00:12:51.480 --> 00:12:53.279
Does the Boss have to report to you?

00:12:53.480 --> 00:12:54.480
Four-eyes.

00:12:58.320 --> 00:12:59.320
Come here.

00:12:59.480 --> 00:13:00.879
Brother Ma, could you please

00:13:01.399 --> 00:13:02.399
give this

00:13:02.759 --> 00:13:03.759
to the Boss's wife?

00:13:04.240 --> 00:13:05.960
It's a calming powder my dad made.

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:07.480
And this

00:13:07.720 --> 00:13:08.720
is the answer she wanted.

00:13:12.200 --> 00:13:13.360
Do you really think

00:13:14.159 --> 00:13:16.200
that going out with the Boss a few times

00:13:17.480 --> 00:13:18.480
makes you a big shot?

00:13:20.159 --> 00:13:21.279
Do you know who she is?

00:13:21.720 --> 00:13:22.639
You think she'll just take medicine

00:13:22.679 --> 00:13:23.679
from some random nobody?

00:13:25.039 --> 00:13:26.279
You little punk.

00:13:32.519 --> 00:13:35.600
She asked for it herself?

00:13:40.519 --> 00:13:41.519
Pay up, pay up!

00:13:41.960 --> 00:13:43.120
I'm in a good mood today,

00:13:44.799 --> 00:13:45.799
so I'll let you off easy.

00:13:47.919 --> 00:13:48.919
Thanks, Brother Ma.

00:13:52.480 --> 00:13:53.480
Go do your job.

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:57.320
Hurry up!

00:13:58.720 --> 00:13:59.200
Deal the cards.

00:13:59.519 --> 00:14:00.039
Let's keep going.

00:14:00.240 --> 00:14:02.120
Money! Give me the money!

00:14:22.039 --> 00:14:23.039
It's a love letter.

00:14:23.080 --> 00:14:24.080
Love...

00:14:32.720 --> 00:14:33.720
Boss.

00:14:34.080 --> 00:14:34.559
Just now,

00:14:35.080 --> 00:14:36.080
that college kid

00:14:36.159 --> 00:14:37.519
asked me to give a letter to your wife.

00:14:38.759 --> 00:14:39.759
The lead actor said

00:14:41.519 --> 00:14:42.600
it's a love letter.

00:14:42.879 --> 00:14:43.960
What kind of crap are you talking?

00:14:44.200 --> 00:14:45.200
Get out!

00:15:13.559 --> 00:15:14.559
Sister.

00:15:16.039 --> 00:15:17.039
It's me,

00:15:17.519 --> 00:15:18.519
Liuyi.

00:15:25.039 --> 00:15:26.039
Liuyi.

00:15:26.960 --> 00:15:27.960
You're here.

00:15:32.039 --> 00:15:33.519
I've been collecting from some shops lately.

00:15:33.639 --> 00:15:35.519
The owner of Guanshansong gave me a bunch of stuff.

00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:37.000
Do you like it?

00:15:40.519 --> 00:15:41.519
What's wrong?

00:15:42.279 --> 00:15:43.399
Why haven't you been at the shrine lately?

00:15:43.399 --> 00:15:44.399
You should stay there for a few days.

00:15:46.879 --> 00:15:48.480
None of you are ever there.

00:15:49.240 --> 00:15:51.279
I don't want to live there alone.

00:15:53.200 --> 00:15:54.200
Where's Brother?

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:55.480
Isn't he staying with you?

00:15:59.679 --> 00:16:01.559
He just pops in occasionally

00:16:02.919 --> 00:16:04.240
and then disappears for a long time.

00:16:06.600 --> 00:16:07.240
Brother...

00:16:07.279 --> 00:16:09.039
He's like a seagull.

00:16:11.720 --> 00:16:12.960
He's a very busy man.

00:16:18.120 --> 00:16:19.120
What about you?

00:16:21.000 --> 00:16:22.120
You're busy too.

00:16:24.559 --> 00:16:26.080
You never come to see me.

00:16:27.639 --> 00:16:28.639
Is it because...

00:16:29.279 --> 00:16:30.919
Because you think I'm sick

00:16:31.000 --> 00:16:32.000
and won't recognize you?

00:16:32.399 --> 00:16:32.799
No.

00:16:32.879 --> 00:16:33.879
That's not it.

00:16:34.320 --> 00:16:35.720
I didn't mean to.

00:16:35.879 --> 00:16:38.519
I... I don't know what happened.

00:16:40.039 --> 00:16:41.559
You were just in shock.

00:16:41.639 --> 00:16:42.639
It wasn't your fault.

00:16:48.720 --> 00:16:50.360
Ma'am, it's time for your medicine.

00:17:07.300 --> 00:17:09.079
I've been listening to the doctor lately.

00:17:09.359 --> 00:17:10.359
I take my medicine on time.

00:17:10.680 --> 00:17:12.480
I'll get better soon.

00:17:14.960 --> 00:17:15.960
Good girl.

00:17:18.079 --> 00:17:18.759
Liuyi,

00:17:18.839 --> 00:17:19.839
you know,

00:17:20.160 --> 00:17:21.160
actually,

00:17:22.039 --> 00:17:23.200
I'm not really sick.

00:17:24.599 --> 00:17:25.599
I

00:17:26.240 --> 00:17:28.400
just get a little anxious.

00:17:31.400 --> 00:17:32.599
It bothers me

00:17:33.279 --> 00:17:35.000
that I have to take medicine so often.

00:17:36.240 --> 00:17:37.240
And it bothers me

00:17:37.680 --> 00:17:38.680
that I

00:17:39.160 --> 00:17:40.400
get anxious so easily.

00:17:41.079 --> 00:17:43.359
It bothers me that he never comes to see me.

00:17:43.920 --> 00:17:45.000
And it bothers me that...

00:17:49.960 --> 00:17:50.960
What is it?

00:17:53.200 --> 00:17:54.480
He doesn't love me.

00:17:59.960 --> 00:18:00.960
He doesn't.

00:18:01.519 --> 00:18:02.519
How could that be?

00:18:09.759 --> 00:18:11.200
Brother Chengqing, you don't love me.

00:18:12.599 --> 00:18:13.359
I'm Liuyi.

00:18:13.599 --> 00:18:14.599
Sister!

00:18:16.519 --> 00:18:17.519
Brother Chengqing,

00:18:17.839 --> 00:18:19.119
you say you love me,

00:18:20.359 --> 00:18:23.000
but why do you rarely hold me?

00:18:24.960 --> 00:18:26.599
When you do hold me,

00:18:27.359 --> 00:18:29.359
I look closely at you.

00:18:32.319 --> 00:18:34.400
Your soul isn't here.

00:18:36.519 --> 00:18:37.680
Your eyes...

00:18:39.519 --> 00:18:42.400
It's like they're looking
at someone else far away.

00:18:43.640 --> 00:18:44.720
You don't love me.

00:18:45.960 --> 00:18:47.000
Where is your soul?

00:18:47.640 --> 00:18:48.119
Sister!

00:18:48.160 --> 00:18:49.480
Your soul has flown away,

00:18:49.799 --> 00:18:50.920
just like that seagull.

00:18:50.920 --> 00:18:51.920
I'm Liuyi.

00:18:52.400 --> 00:18:52.720
Sister!

00:18:53.119 --> 00:18:54.279
You don't love me.

00:18:55.279 --> 00:18:57.160
If you don't love me, why did you marry me?

00:18:57.279 --> 00:18:57.640
Sister!

00:18:58.119 --> 00:18:59.119
Why?

00:18:59.160 --> 00:19:00.480
Who is it that you really love?

00:19:01.559 --> 00:19:02.559
Sister!

00:19:03.160 --> 00:19:04.160
Sister, it's me.

00:19:04.640 --> 00:19:05.640
I'm Liuyi.

00:19:13.000 --> 00:19:13.680
I'm Liuyi!

00:19:13.920 --> 00:19:14.480
Liuyi?

00:19:14.880 --> 00:19:15.880
Liuyi...

00:19:19.640 --> 00:19:20.640
It's okay now.

00:19:23.759 --> 00:19:24.759
Li... Liuyi.

00:19:28.359 --> 00:19:29.359
I...

00:19:30.160 --> 00:19:31.160
I...

00:19:31.640 --> 00:19:32.640
I...

00:19:33.079 --> 00:19:33.880
Did I just...?

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:34.880
It's okay.

00:19:35.799 --> 00:19:36.799
It's okay, it's okay.

00:20:09.359 --> 00:20:11.119
Brother Chengqing, you don't love me.

00:20:12.200 --> 00:20:13.319
Your eyes...

00:20:14.960 --> 00:20:17.920
It's like they're looking at someone else far away.

00:20:19.480 --> 00:20:19.960
Boss,

00:20:20.200 --> 00:20:21.200
Brother Liuyi is waiting for you.

00:20:25.960 --> 00:20:26.960
What are you doing here?

00:20:32.640 --> 00:20:33.839
I heard you were hurt.

00:20:41.599 --> 00:20:42.799
Why don't you stay here tonight?

00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:44.200
You can take the guest room.

00:20:53.799 --> 00:20:54.799
Brother,

00:20:56.720 --> 00:20:57.920
is there someone else?

00:20:59.279 --> 00:21:00.480
What are you talking about?

00:21:03.039 --> 00:21:04.319
Sister says you don't love her.

00:21:05.319 --> 00:21:06.519
She says your heart
belongs to someone else.

00:21:14.240 --> 00:21:15.240
Do you remember

00:21:17.079 --> 00:21:18.519
what you said when you
begged me to marry Xiaoman?

00:21:20.720 --> 00:21:21.720
Do you?

00:21:32.160 --> 00:21:33.279
You're almost twenty.

00:21:33.720 --> 00:21:34.759
What do you want for your birthday?

00:21:35.880 --> 00:21:37.359
Will you give me anything I want?

00:21:37.599 --> 00:21:38.599
Of course.

00:21:38.799 --> 00:21:39.880
You know I'd do anything for you.

00:21:43.079 --> 00:21:44.079
I want

00:21:46.519 --> 00:21:47.680
Xiaoman to be my sister-in-law.

00:21:53.079 --> 00:21:54.079
You said

00:21:56.039 --> 00:21:57.359
you wanted the three of us

00:21:58.960 --> 00:22:00.480
to be a real family

00:22:01.480 --> 00:22:02.640
and stay together forever.

00:22:05.160 --> 00:22:06.160
I agreed

00:22:08.240 --> 00:22:09.240
because

00:22:11.680 --> 00:22:12.799
that's what I wanted too.

00:22:14.119 --> 00:22:15.119
And

00:22:15.920 --> 00:22:17.039
that's all I wanted.

00:22:19.799 --> 00:22:21.400
So don't ever say that again.

00:22:31.406 --> 00:22:33.486
There's a nice Western
restaurant in Tsin Shui Wan.

00:22:34.960 --> 00:22:36.200
I'll take her there in a few days.

00:22:40.200 --> 00:22:41.200
Brother...

00:22:45.200 --> 00:22:46.200
Brother,

00:22:53.799 --> 00:22:55.240
can't you just truly love her?

00:23:14.119 --> 00:23:15.319
Nice tie today.

00:23:41.720 --> 00:23:43.039
It's been a week.

00:23:43.680 --> 00:23:45.119
A whole week without any filming.

00:23:45.960 --> 00:23:47.240
Xia Liuyi hasn't shown up either.

00:23:48.119 --> 00:23:49.039
I have no idea

00:23:49.039 --> 00:23:50.400
when I can go back to school.

00:23:51.559 --> 00:23:52.599
If I don't go back soon,

00:23:53.079 --> 00:23:54.480
they'll probably expel me.

00:24:04.279 --> 00:24:04.759
Brother Liuyi,

00:24:05.079 --> 00:24:06.079
you're here.

00:24:08.359 --> 00:24:09.839
Brother Liuyi, you're really good at pool.

00:24:12.319 --> 00:24:13.319
Watch closely.

00:24:22.480 --> 00:24:23.480
I'm watching.

00:24:29.839 --> 00:24:30.839
How is it?

00:24:33.480 --> 00:24:34.480
Well?

00:24:37.240 --> 00:24:38.240
How's your injury?

00:24:39.559 --> 00:24:40.559
Are you blind?

00:24:40.799 --> 00:24:41.799
Stop talking nonsense.

00:24:41.960 --> 00:24:43.559
What about your sister?

00:24:46.839 --> 00:24:47.839
What are you getting at?

00:24:50.279 --> 00:24:51.880
My dad gave me a new doctor...

00:24:52.960 --> 00:24:53.359
No,

00:24:53.559 --> 00:24:54.680
my dad gave me a new

00:24:54.680 --> 00:24:56.160
prescription for calming the nerves.

00:24:56.519 --> 00:24:58.680
And some medicine for healing bruises.

00:24:59.400 --> 00:25:00.480
It's for you and your sister.

00:25:01.359 --> 00:25:02.000
I don't know

00:25:02.359 --> 00:25:03.480
if you'll find it useful.

00:25:14.200 --> 00:25:16.279
I knew something was up with you.

00:25:16.519 --> 00:25:17.519
Do you have a crush on my sister?

00:25:17.519 --> 00:25:17.920
No!

00:25:18.200 --> 00:25:19.200
Then why are you being so nice to her?

00:25:19.880 --> 00:25:21.000
I heard that while I was away,

00:25:21.000 --> 00:25:22.400
you were asking everyone about her.

00:25:24.519 --> 00:25:26.880
I was just worried about both of you.

00:25:28.599 --> 00:25:29.599
Liuyi,

00:25:31.279 --> 00:25:32.480
are you bullying Chusan again?

00:25:33.319 --> 00:25:34.319
No.

00:25:34.680 --> 00:25:35.680
No, not at all.

00:25:36.839 --> 00:25:37.920
Chusan, are you okay?

00:25:38.640 --> 00:25:40.079
It's just my ear...

00:25:41.799 --> 00:25:43.039
My ear is a bit thick.

00:25:44.000 --> 00:25:45.000
It doesn't hurt.

00:25:45.599 --> 00:25:46.680
Yeah, Sister,

00:25:46.960 --> 00:25:48.359
we were just messing around.

00:25:48.519 --> 00:25:49.519
Right?

00:25:49.920 --> 00:25:50.920
Right, Chusan?

00:25:53.400 --> 00:25:54.400
What's this?

00:25:56.200 --> 00:25:57.200
These are for you.

00:25:57.960 --> 00:25:58.567
Supplements.

00:25:58.799 --> 00:25:59.799
They're health supplements.

00:26:00.720 --> 00:26:01.720
Sister,

00:26:02.000 --> 00:26:03.240
you look beautiful today.

00:26:04.240 --> 00:26:04.759
Really?

00:26:05.039 --> 00:26:06.039
Yes.

00:26:06.920 --> 00:26:08.920
Brother Chengqing is taking me to a Western restaurant

00:26:08.920 --> 00:26:09.920
for steak today.

00:26:10.799 --> 00:26:12.359
The steak there is delicious.

00:26:12.839 --> 00:26:14.480
Chusan, do you like steak?

00:26:17.079 --> 00:26:18.079
I've never had it.

00:26:19.559 --> 00:26:20.599
Western food is too expensive.

00:26:20.880 --> 00:26:23.079
One meal would cost me

00:26:23.839 --> 00:26:24.839
a whole month's allowance.

00:26:27.160 --> 00:26:28.960
Then why don't you come with us?

00:26:29.480 --> 00:26:30.480
Brother Chengqing will pay.

00:26:30.720 --> 00:26:31.720
Consider it a thank-you for the letter.

00:26:34.720 --> 00:26:35.720
No way.

00:26:36.759 --> 00:26:37.279
Liuyi,

00:26:37.680 --> 00:26:38.680
be more generous with your friends.

00:26:38.920 --> 00:26:39.759
It's not that, Sister.

00:26:39.759 --> 00:26:41.279
It's not about being generous.

00:26:46.039 --> 00:26:46.839
Let's go together.

00:26:47.000 --> 00:26:48.000
There's plenty of room.

00:26:50.160 --> 00:26:51.160
Come on.

00:26:52.000 --> 00:26:53.000
Let's go.

00:27:06.400 --> 00:27:07.960
I didn't ask to come.

00:27:16.839 --> 00:27:17.839
Let's go!

00:27:25.200 --> 00:27:26.200
Please come again.

00:27:32.640 --> 00:27:33.640
Good evening, Mr. Hao.

00:27:33.832 --> 00:27:35.673
You reserved a Christmas-themed table for two.

00:27:35.839 --> 00:27:37.480
Should I change that to a table for four?

00:27:40.680 --> 00:27:41.799
We can just sit over there.

00:27:42.279 --> 00:27:43.279
Sister, Brother,

00:27:43.359 --> 00:27:44.480
you two sit there.

00:27:45.599 --> 00:27:46.039
Okay.

00:27:46.359 --> 00:27:47.680
It's rare to see you make a friend.

00:27:48.319 --> 00:27:49.319
Take good care of Chusan.

00:27:50.200 --> 00:27:50.599
Will do.

00:27:50.960 --> 00:27:51.960
This way.

00:27:53.160 --> 00:27:54.160
Let's go over there.

00:28:27.960 --> 00:28:28.960
Tell me,

00:28:29.880 --> 00:28:30.880
don't they look perfect together?

00:28:36.240 --> 00:28:37.240
If you don't know how to use those,

00:28:37.599 --> 00:28:38.799
just use your hands.

00:28:44.839 --> 00:28:45.839
Excuse me.

00:28:47.240 --> 00:28:48.240
Can we get some chopsticks?

00:28:48.480 --> 00:28:49.839
Sir, this is a Western restaurant.

00:28:50.039 --> 00:28:51.319
Nobody uses chopsticks for Western food.

00:28:52.599 --> 00:28:53.599
Chopsticks.

00:28:53.720 --> 00:28:54.319
Do you understand?

00:28:54.640 --> 00:28:55.680
We're Chinese.

00:28:55.680 --> 00:28:56.839
We should use chopsticks when we eat.

00:28:57.079 --> 00:28:58.319
Very well, sir. One moment.

00:29:01.400 --> 00:29:02.640
You talk too much.

00:29:07.559 --> 00:29:08.559
Xia Liuyi,

00:29:09.359 --> 00:29:10.359
thank you.

00:29:15.720 --> 00:29:17.119
And thanks for saving me the other day.

00:29:25.519 --> 00:29:26.960
Don't flatter yourself.

00:29:27.839 --> 00:29:28.960
You're working for me,

00:29:29.480 --> 00:29:30.759
so that makes you my lackey.

00:29:31.473 --> 00:29:32.552
Taking care of my brothers

00:29:32.880 --> 00:29:33.880
is what a boss does.

00:29:33.880 --> 00:29:34.880
(I am not your lackey.)

00:29:36.160 --> 00:29:37.160
Once I finish this script,

00:29:38.039 --> 00:29:39.559
we're done.

00:29:40.200 --> 00:29:42.039
Even if you were dying in the street,

00:29:42.039 --> 00:29:43.119
I wouldn't give you a second look.

00:29:46.599 --> 00:29:47.599
Your chopsticks, sir.

00:29:55.759 --> 00:29:56.599
Thug.

00:29:56.599 --> 00:29:57.240
Brute.

00:29:57.480 --> 00:29:58.319
Wolf in sheep's clothing.

00:29:58.319 --> 00:29:59.000
Monster.

00:29:59.000 --> 00:30:00.000
Heartless bastard.

00:30:04.359 --> 00:30:06.720
He Chusan,

00:30:06.799 --> 00:30:08.039
it's still good if you pick
it up in three seconds.

00:30:17.559 --> 00:30:18.559
Brother Chengqing,

00:30:18.799 --> 00:30:20.119
it's so beautiful here today.

00:30:21.920 --> 00:30:22.920
Do you remember?

00:30:23.279 --> 00:30:24.359
Actually, you've

00:30:24.519 --> 00:30:25.559
brought me here before.

00:30:26.200 --> 00:30:27.039
Back then,

00:30:27.160 --> 00:30:28.200
we spent Christmas together.

00:30:28.759 --> 00:30:30.640
We had a barbecue nearby

00:30:30.799 --> 00:30:31.799
and set off fireworks.

00:30:32.400 --> 00:30:33.720
Liuyi was being so mischievous,

00:30:34.119 --> 00:30:35.200
he even got burned by a firework.

00:30:42.720 --> 00:30:43.839
I'm not bringing you next time.

00:30:44.240 --> 00:30:45.240
I'm sorry.

00:30:45.519 --> 00:30:46.359
You got it on my clothes.

00:30:46.400 --> 00:30:47.640
This shirt was expensive.

00:30:47.799 --> 00:30:48.799
I'll wash it for you.

00:30:49.160 --> 00:30:50.160
I'm so sorry.

00:30:50.659 --> 00:30:52.160
Liuyi is still as mischievous as ever.

00:30:54.240 --> 00:30:55.240
Yeah.

00:30:55.319 --> 00:30:56.319
That kid's temper

00:30:56.640 --> 00:30:58.200
is getting more and more out of control.

00:31:02.400 --> 00:31:03.400
Brother Chengqing,

00:31:06.000 --> 00:31:07.359
am I a bit boring?

00:31:09.079 --> 00:31:10.079
Of course not.

00:31:10.720 --> 00:31:11.720
Why would you think that?

00:31:14.839 --> 00:31:15.640
Is it the steak?

00:31:15.640 --> 00:31:16.640
Is it not to your liking?

00:31:17.000 --> 00:31:18.000
Try some of mine.

00:31:33.599 --> 00:31:34.599
Brother Chengqing,

00:31:37.559 --> 00:31:38.559
let's get a divorce.

00:31:43.920 --> 00:31:45.200
Are you feeling okay?

00:31:45.559 --> 00:31:46.559
Did you bring your medicine?

00:31:52.880 --> 00:31:53.880
No.

00:31:55.480 --> 00:31:56.480
I'm perfectly lucid.

00:31:57.920 --> 00:31:58.920
And I'm very calm.

00:32:00.839 --> 00:32:01.839
You...

00:32:02.039 --> 00:32:03.039
You don't love me.

00:32:10.279 --> 00:32:11.279
If our marriage

00:32:13.839 --> 00:32:15.920
is just one-sided on my part,

00:32:18.119 --> 00:32:19.359
then it's a mistake.

00:32:25.240 --> 00:32:25.599
Xiaoman...

00:32:25.839 --> 00:32:26.839
I've known for a long time.

00:32:28.559 --> 00:32:30.279
I just didn't want to admit it.

00:32:31.960 --> 00:32:32.960
I thought

00:32:33.480 --> 00:32:34.480
that since I love you

00:32:36.200 --> 00:32:37.839
and you've always been so good to me,

00:32:41.759 --> 00:32:43.680
we would surely be happy.

00:32:46.400 --> 00:32:47.400
But I was wrong.

00:32:50.720 --> 00:32:51.960
Love isn't just what you see.

00:32:54.680 --> 00:32:55.680
It's what you feel in your heart.

00:33:13.319 --> 00:33:14.319
You're good to me

00:33:15.200 --> 00:33:16.240
because we're family.

00:33:20.279 --> 00:33:21.400
But what I want...

00:33:26.119 --> 00:33:27.559
What I want is romantic love.

00:33:28.960 --> 00:33:29.960
I'm sorry.

00:33:33.480 --> 00:33:35.680
You didn't have to admit it so quickly.

00:33:38.079 --> 00:33:39.079
Couldn't you have

00:33:41.160 --> 00:33:42.160
just lied to me for a bit?

00:33:46.640 --> 00:33:47.640
I'm sorry.

00:33:50.720 --> 00:33:50.960
You...

00:33:51.359 --> 00:33:52.640
You don't need to apologize.

00:33:55.480 --> 00:33:56.279
In the beginning,

00:33:56.279 --> 00:33:57.599
I never even asked how you felt.

00:33:58.920 --> 00:34:00.160
I'm the one who dragged us both

00:34:00.160 --> 00:34:01.480
into this situation.

00:34:06.279 --> 00:34:07.400
Liuyi won't agree to this.

00:34:19.280 --> 00:34:20.280
Liuyi...

00:34:23.119 --> 00:34:24.840
He's just too worried about me.

00:34:30.599 --> 00:34:31.599
All this time,

00:34:33.880 --> 00:34:35.280
even though I'm the older sister,

00:34:39.760 --> 00:34:42.199
he's the one who's been protecting me

00:34:44.559 --> 00:34:46.199
and giving me everything I need.

00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:53.559
Let's wait until the movie is finished.

00:34:59.239 --> 00:35:00.320
Once filming is over,

00:35:02.760 --> 00:35:03.960
I'll tell him.

00:35:07.480 --> 00:35:08.480
I'll tell him with you.

00:35:15.679 --> 00:35:16.679
Brother Chengqing,

00:35:17.840 --> 00:35:18.840
can you

00:35:20.920 --> 00:35:22.559
tell me who it is

00:35:23.800 --> 00:35:24.800
that you really love?

00:35:30.039 --> 00:35:31.039
I'm sorry.

00:35:38.320 --> 00:35:39.320
Hao Chengqing,

00:35:41.239 --> 00:35:42.360
you really are a bastard.

00:36:02.920 --> 00:36:04.519
Alright, alright, don't rush.

00:36:04.800 --> 00:36:07.119
Everyone will get one.

00:36:07.920 --> 00:36:08.960
This one's yours.

00:36:08.960 --> 00:36:09.960
Take your time.

00:36:11.480 --> 00:36:12.199
Thank you, thank you.

00:36:12.400 --> 00:36:13.400
Come back if you like it!

00:36:13.960 --> 00:36:14.519
Thanks a lot.

00:36:14.880 --> 00:36:15.760
What's going on here?

00:36:15.840 --> 00:36:16.480
Why is it so crowded?

00:36:16.519 --> 00:36:17.599
There's a new movie coming out.

00:36:17.760 --> 00:36:18.760
I heard it's pretty good.

00:36:19.280 --> 00:36:19.840
Is that so?

00:36:19.960 --> 00:36:20.960
Look at this.

00:36:22.519 --> 00:36:25.599
Heroic Shadows.

00:36:26.000 --> 00:36:27.760
Starring Xia Xiaoman.

00:36:29.842 --> 00:36:31.622
(Executive Producer: Xia Liuyi
Scriptwriter: He Chusan)

00:36:32.519 --> 00:36:33.280
Do you want to see it?

00:36:33.320 --> 00:36:34.320
Not really.

00:36:35.519 --> 00:36:37.039
You should go with your dad.

00:36:37.280 --> 00:36:38.280
It'll be fun.

00:36:38.400 --> 00:36:39.039
Look,

00:36:39.239 --> 00:36:41.000
Produced by Xia Liuyi.

00:36:42.719 --> 00:36:43.719
Fei Jie,

00:36:46.400 --> 00:36:47.639
my dad loves Cantonese opera.

00:36:48.119 --> 00:36:49.280
He's not into these modern movies.

00:36:50.079 --> 00:36:51.079
I heard

00:36:51.519 --> 00:36:53.719
that the Walled City Temple is putting on

00:36:53.760 --> 00:36:55.159
The Reincarnation of the Red Plum tonight.

00:36:55.840 --> 00:36:57.039
If my dad knew,

00:36:57.360 --> 00:36:58.880
he'd be thrilled.

00:36:58.960 --> 00:36:59.480
Really?

00:36:59.559 --> 00:36:59.920
Yeah.

00:36:59.960 --> 00:37:00.960
Do I have time to change?

00:37:01.119 --> 00:37:02.119
Yes, it starts at seven.

00:37:02.679 --> 00:37:03.079
Is that right?

00:37:03.079 --> 00:37:03.480
Yes.

00:37:03.920 --> 00:37:06.159
But this actress is very pretty.

00:37:07.239 --> 00:37:07.679
Let's go, let's go.

00:37:07.679 --> 00:37:08.480
Look, Boss.

00:37:08.599 --> 00:37:09.719
So many flower baskets.

00:37:10.639 --> 00:37:11.639
Boss,

00:37:12.159 --> 00:37:15.480
half the big shots in Hong Kong
are here today for the premiere.

00:37:16.760 --> 00:37:17.760
Boss,

00:37:17.880 --> 00:37:18.880
are they going to announce

00:37:19.320 --> 00:37:20.320
that you're the new Young Master of the Hall?

00:37:21.480 --> 00:37:22.760
Don't talk nonsense.

00:37:23.239 --> 00:37:24.239
I'm telling you,

00:37:24.559 --> 00:37:25.559
they

00:37:25.719 --> 00:37:27.280
all invested in this movie.

00:37:27.920 --> 00:37:30.559
They're here because they want their share of the box office.

00:37:30.599 --> 00:37:31.760
Of course they'd show up.

00:37:32.039 --> 00:37:33.079
What Young Master?

00:37:33.079 --> 00:37:34.079
Stop talking trash.

00:37:34.400 --> 00:37:36.559
If I catch you spreading rumors,

00:37:37.159 --> 00:37:39.000
I'll cut your tongue out. Understand?

00:37:40.840 --> 00:37:42.599
Well, the movie is about to open.

00:37:42.880 --> 00:37:43.480
That madam

00:37:43.719 --> 00:37:45.480
is going to be famous all over the city.

00:37:45.719 --> 00:37:46.719
That's right, that's right.

00:37:47.719 --> 00:37:48.719
Of course.

00:37:49.840 --> 00:37:51.039
Sister will be so happy.

00:37:51.880 --> 00:37:52.679
And the Boss...

00:37:52.760 --> 00:37:53.760
he'll be happy too.

00:37:55.360 --> 00:37:56.360
It's almost time.

00:37:56.920 --> 00:37:58.079
I'm going to pick up Brother and Sister.

00:37:58.679 --> 00:37:59.719
You guys keep an eye on things here.

00:38:00.679 --> 00:38:01.480
Don't worry.

00:38:01.559 --> 00:38:02.559
We've got it.

00:38:04.760 --> 00:38:05.760
Alright, this way.

00:38:06.000 --> 00:38:06.559
Come on, come on.

00:38:06.559 --> 00:38:08.199
Take good care of the investors.

00:38:33.360 --> 00:38:34.360
Brother!

00:38:37.159 --> 00:38:38.159
Sister!

00:38:47.000 --> 00:38:48.000
Brother!

00:38:54.159 --> 00:38:55.159
Sister!

00:39:00.400 --> 00:39:01.400
Sister!

00:39:01.800 --> 00:39:02.800
Ahao...

00:39:04.320 --> 00:39:04.559
Sister!

00:39:04.559 --> 00:39:05.559
Don't come any closer!

00:39:05.960 --> 00:39:06.960
Get down from there!

00:39:07.519 --> 00:39:08.519
Get down, Sister!

00:39:09.719 --> 00:39:10.719
Come here.

00:39:11.320 --> 00:39:12.320
Don't scare me like this, Sister.

00:39:13.199 --> 00:39:14.400
Sister, what's wrong?

00:39:14.920 --> 00:39:15.920
Please, come back.

00:39:23.480 --> 00:39:24.480
Sister!

00:39:27.559 --> 00:39:28.559
Sister!

00:39:36.880 --> 00:39:38.760
Sister!

00:40:01.559 --> 00:40:02.559
Liuyi...

00:40:06.159 --> 00:40:07.159
Liuyi!

00:40:07.360 --> 00:40:08.360
Brother!

00:40:12.039 --> 00:40:13.039
Brother!

00:40:13.559 --> 00:40:14.559
Brother!

00:40:18.880 --> 00:40:20.320
Aren't these my Green Dragon twin blades?

00:40:26.320 --> 00:40:27.320
Brother,

00:40:28.159 --> 00:40:29.159
I'm getting you out of here.

00:40:31.519 --> 00:40:32.519
Lean on me.

00:43:17.280 --> 00:43:18.639
Xia Liuyi!

00:43:21.000 --> 00:43:22.239
I thought you were so tough.

00:43:22.599 --> 00:43:24.840
Aren't you the top enforcer?

00:43:25.559 --> 00:43:27.000
If you've got the guts, come out

00:43:27.159 --> 00:43:29.880
and collect your brother and sister's bodies.

00:43:30.840 --> 00:43:32.159
I really want to see

00:43:32.679 --> 00:43:34.000
which is faster—your blade

00:43:34.559 --> 00:43:36.159
or my bullet.

00:43:56.880 --> 00:43:57.880
Infuriating.

00:43:59.159 --> 00:44:00.159
Spread the word.

00:44:00.639 --> 00:44:02.760
Xia Liuyi killed the Green Dragon boss

00:44:03.079 --> 00:44:04.880
and drove his crazy sister to jump.

00:44:06.159 --> 00:44:08.920
The whole Xiaoqi Hall is out to catch the traitor.

00:44:09.840 --> 00:44:11.400
Dead or alive.

00:44:11.519 --> 00:44:12.519
Yes, sir!

00:44:29.360 --> 00:44:30.360
Don't move.

00:44:37.320 --> 00:44:38.320
Don't make a sound.

00:44:41.880 --> 00:44:43.239
Get me some styptic powder

00:44:45.119 --> 00:44:46.119
and some gauze.

00:44:47.639 --> 00:44:48.639
Yes.

00:44:48.920 --> 00:44:49.920
Xia Liuyi?

00:44:57.719 --> 00:45:00.599
It really is you, you bastard.